high_descs: Turn left, walk to the counter, turn right, walk to the coffee pot.
Pick up the coffee cup on the coffee pot.
Walk to the right to the fridge.
Put the coffee cup next to the bowl in the fridge for a few seconds, take the coffee cup back out.
Take a step to the right.
Put the coffee cup in the last bottom cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place the cold coffee cup in the cabinet.

high_descs: Move to the coffee maker to the left of the fridge
Pick up mug from the coffee maker
Move to the fridge to the right of you
Chill the mug for a moment in the fridge before grabbing it and close the door
Move to the cabinet to the left of the fridge
Put the mug inside and close the door
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug in the bottom cabinet closest to the fridge.

high_descs: turn left, turn right, walk to the coffee machine
grab the cup in the coffee machine
turn right, walk to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator, put the cup in for a while, take the cup out
walk to the left a little
open the end cabinet, put the cup in
anns.task_desc: cool the cup in the refrigerator, put the cup in the cabinet
